{"name": "Gauntlet", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_50.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A reinforced gauntlet designed for combat, capable of delivering powerful blows while keeping the hand protected.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Finesse</td><td>Melee d4 (B/P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Deflect, Disarm, Nimble, Riposte</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When hit with a melee attack, as a reaction before damage is dealt, attempt a Disarm. If you successfully disarm the attacker, you take no damage and possess the weapon."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Cane Sword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_34.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A gentleman's walking cane that conceals a slender blade, equally useful as a social accessory and a deadly weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse</td><td>Melee d6 (B/P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Entangle, Puncture, Riposte, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 35, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "While dual wielding the cane and sword together, the cane gains Deflect d8. Hitting with the cane deals your DEX modifier in damage (minimum 1), and you gain advantage on your next attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Compass Blade", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_33.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A precision-engineered clockwork throwing blade that unfolds in flight, making it deadly at range as well as in melee.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse</td><td>Melee 2d4 (P/S), Thrown 2d4 (40/60)</td><td>Clockwork, Keen, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 100, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When deployed as a Double Ended attack, the attack gains advantage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Hidden Blade", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_38.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A clockwork wrist-mounted blade that deploys on demand, ideal for assassination and ambush.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Finesse</td><td>Melee d4 (P)</td><td>Clockwork, Conceal, Nimble, Slip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Surprised creatures take maximum damage from this weapon and any attachments."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Knuckle Axe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_29.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact axe blade mounted on a knuckle guard, combining the striking power of an axe with the mobility of a fist weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (P/S)</td><td>Deflect, Conceal, Keen</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you reduce a creature to 0 HP, make one additional attack. When wielding two knuckle axes, extra attacks also trigger on a critical hit. Once per attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Interceptor", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_48.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A hardened parrying device worn on the forearm or hand, designed primarily to intercept attacks and deflect incoming blows.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Finesse</td><td>Melee (B)</td><td>Conceal, Deflect (d6)</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Deflect can be used against ranged weapon attacks. When you can see a target within 5 feet, use your reaction to impose disadvantage on their attack roll."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Katar", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_47.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A push dagger with a horizontal hand grip, allowing the wielder to punch with lethal force and cut with exceptional control.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Keen, Nimble</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you score a powerful blow (critical hit), make one additional attack as part of the same action. If dual wielding katars, this extra attack also activates for the off-hand katar."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Punch Dagger", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_44.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A tiny blade mounted horizontally across the knuckles, making it nearly invisible in the hand and ideal for close-quarters ambushes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P)</td><td>Conceal, Nimble, Punch</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You have advantage on attacks made outside of your turn. If wielding this weapon in your off-hand, you may make an opportunity attack with both weapons."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Side Baton", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_42.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A short baton with a perpendicular side handle, granting exceptional leverage for blocking and striking.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (B)</td><td>Deflect, Riposte</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "+1 to weapon AC. Deflect increases to d10, and you may add your proficiency bonus to Deflect rolls."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Fan", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_36.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An ornate war fan with razor-edged metal tines, capable of being used folded as a bludgeon or unfolded as a slashing and piercing weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (B/P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Keen, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>While unfolded:</em> Deflect 2d6 vs ranged attacks. <em>While folded:</em> Gains Stagger and Melee d6.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Ambush Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "While unfolded, Deflect increases to 2d6 against ranged attacks. While folded, the fan gains Stagger and its melee damage becomes d6."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Battle Axe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_04.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A reliable single-bladed axe sized for one-handed use, capable of devastating sweeping blows and powerful two-handed grip.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Versatile</td><td>Melee d8 (S), Versatile d10</td><td>Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": "battleaxe"}, "properties": ["ver"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Reroll 1s and 2s on damage dice. When wielded two-handed, the axe also gains Thrown with a damage die of d12 (20/60 ft range)."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Broadaxe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_05.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A wide-headed two-handed axe designed for maximum cutting surface, ideal for cleaving through armor and shield alike.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy</td><td>Melee 2d6 (S)</td><td>Punch, Sunder</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On a mighty blow (critical hit), the target is Staggered and cannot make a saving throw to resist the condition."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Greataxe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_10.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive two-handed axe that trades subtlety for raw destructive power, capable of felling enemies and disarming them in one sweep.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy</td><td>Melee d12 (S)</td><td>Disarm, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 20, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": "greataxe"}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On a mighty blow (critical hit), add one additional damage die to the total damage dealt."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Halberd", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_08.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A pole weapon combining an axe blade with a spear tip and hook, offering versatile attack options at extended reach.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach</td><td>Melee 2d6 (P/S)</td><td>Brace, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 35, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 7, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": "halberd"}, "properties": ["hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Trip attacks made with this weapon impose disadvantage on the target's saving throw to resist being knocked prone."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Handaxe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_01.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A small, single-headed axe light enough to be thrown or used as an off-hand weapon, reliable and easy to carry in multiples.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (S), Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": "handaxe"}, "properties": ["lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you miss a Disarm attack, you may reroll the attack and take the new result."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Hook Sword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_06.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A crescent-bladed sword with a hooked tip, excellent for catching enemy weapons and creating openings in combat.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (S)</td><td>Disarm, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Two hook swords can be hooked together to gain Reach and Versatile d8.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 30, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On a melee hit, use your reaction to attempt a Disarm or Entangle as a bonus. When two hook swords are linked together, they gain Reach and deal Versatile d8 damage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Kama", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_03.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A small sickle-like weapon derived from a farming tool, fast and precise enough to be thrown or used in pairs.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P/S), Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Keen, Nimble</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Keen adds 2 extra damage dice instead of 1. An off-hand kama adds its Keen bonus to the main-hand attack as well."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Palm Axe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_02.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive two-handed reaching axe with a broad curved blade, designed to sweep multiple targets in a single action.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach</td><td>Melee 2d6 (P/S)</td><td>Brace, Keen, Puncture, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 45, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As an action, attack each creature within your reach. Until the start of your next turn, ranged attackers suffer disadvantage against you."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Poleaxe", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_25.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A versatile pole weapon bearing axe, hammer, and spike heads, capable of bludgeoning, piercing, slashing, and blocking in a single weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy</td><td>Melee d10 (B/P/S)</td><td>Brace, Deflect, Punch, Puncture, Stagger, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 40, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 7, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "+1 to weapon AC. You may add your proficiency bonus to Deflect rolls made with this weapon."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Tomahawk", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/axes/axe_07.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A light, balanced throwing axe with a broad curved blade, designed for hurling at range as much as fighting in melee.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P/S), Thrown (40/120)</td><td>Slip, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Axes", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On a mighty blow (critical hit), the target has disadvantage on their next attack roll."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bar Mace", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy iron bar fitted with flanges, capable of crushing blows as well as tearing cuts. Favored by warriors who want a weapon that can crack armor and break bones alike.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Bludgeoning or Slashing or Piercing, Disarm</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Bludgeoning or Slashing or Piercing, Disarm, Powerful Blow</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Powerful Blow: deals STR modifier bonus damage and the target has disadvantage on attack rolls; the target makes a CON save to end the effect.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Powerful Blow deals STR modifier bonus damage and the target has disadvantage on attack rolls until they succeed on a CON save to end the effect."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bo Staff", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/staves/staff-simple.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long hardwood staff used in martial arts traditions, wielded with flowing strikes from both ends. Lightweight and deceptively quick in trained hands.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d4, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Double Ended d4, Bludgeoning, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Double Ended d4, Bludgeoning, Trip, enhanced flow attacks</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If you have Extra Attack, you may make two Double Ended attacks instead of one, or make two opportunity attacks instead of one per reaction.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you have Extra Attack, you may make two Double Ended attacks or two opportunity attacks instead of one per reaction."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Flanged Mace", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-flanged-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A mace fitted with multiple steel flanges that slice through gaps in armor. Equally effective at battering shields and shearing mail rings.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Bludgeoning or Slashing, Punch, Sunder</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Bludgeoning or Slashing, Punch, Sunder (enhanced), Powerful Blow</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Sunder always reduces the target's AC by 2 on a failed save. A Powerful Blow automatically triggers a Sunder effect without requiring a save.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Sunder always reduces the target's AC by 2. A Powerful Blow automatically applies the Sunder effect without a save."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Greatclub", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/clubs/club-heavy-barbed.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive wooden or iron-shod club designed to deliver devastating two-handed blows. Crude but terrifyingly effective at smashing through armor and bone.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d6, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Bludgeoning, Disarm, Punch, Stagger, Sunder</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Bludgeoning, Disarm, Punch, Stagger, Sunder, Mighty Blow</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Mighty Blow: the target must succeed on a CON save or suffer permanent disadvantage on all attack rolls until the damaged weapon or armor is repaired.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 8, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Mighty Blow: the target must succeed on a CON save or suffer permanent disadvantage on all attack rolls until the damaged weapon or armor is repaired."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Heavy Club", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/clubs/club-heavy-brown-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A thick, weighted club of dense hardwood, heavy enough to knock a man off his feet when thrown or swung with full force. Versatile enough to be gripped in two hands for extra power.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Versatile 2d4, Thrown (20/40), Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Versatile 2d4, Thrown (20/40), Bludgeoning, Mighty Blow</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Mighty Blow: the target must succeed on a CON save or suffer disadvantage on all attack rolls and ability checks until the end of its next turn.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 40, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["ver", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Mighty Blow: the target must succeed on a CON save or suffer disadvantage on all attack rolls and ability checks until the end of its next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Light Club", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/clubs/club-worn.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A short, slender wooden baton easily concealed beneath a cloak. Quick to draw and light in hand, it delivers sharp rapping blows to joints and skulls with surprising effect.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Bludgeoning, Conceal</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Bludgeoning, Conceal, Mighty Blow</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Mighty Blow: the target must succeed on a CON save or suffer disadvantage on STR, DEX, and WIS saving throws until the end of its next turn.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Mighty Blow: the target must succeed on a CON save or suffer disadvantage on STR, DEX, and WIS saving throws until the end of its next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Mallet", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-war.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy-headed mallet used by craftsmen and soldiers alike. Its flat face can drive spikes or crack skulls, and it flies surprisingly well when hurled with purpose.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Bludgeoning, Disarm</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Bludgeoning, Disarm, bonus shove</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you take the Attack action with this weapon, you may use your bonus action to attempt a shove. On a successful shove, the target also takes weapon damage.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you take the Attack action, you may use your bonus action to shove a target. On a successful shove, the target also takes weapon damage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Morningstar", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-black.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long-hafted weapon with a spiked iron head, combining reach with brutal impact. The spike punches through armor while the weight of the head shatters bones and bends steel.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d8, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Reach, Melee d10, Bludgeoning or Piercing, Brace, Punch, Sunder, Wound</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Reach, Melee d10, Bludgeoning or Piercing, Brace, Punch, Sunder (enhanced), Wound</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When an enemy fails their save against Sunder, their AC is reduced by your STR modifier (minimum 1) instead of the standard amount.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When an enemy fails their save against Sunder, their AC is reduced by your STR modifier (minimum 1) instead of the standard amount."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Quarterstaff", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/staves/staff-ornate-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>The classic fighting staff of soldiers, monks, and wanderers. Wielded with both hands, it delivers rapid two-ended strikes and can trip an opponent in an instant. Masters use it defensively as well as offensively.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d6, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d8, Double Ended d6, Bludgeoning, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d8, Double Ended d6, Bludgeoning, Trip, defensive stance</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You gain +1 to AC while wielding this weapon. When you attack a creature more than 5 feet away (using Reach or Double Ended), the damage die becomes a d10.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "+1 to AC while wielding. When attacking a creature more than 5 feet away, the damage die becomes a d10."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Spiked Mace", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-flanged-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A lightweight mace studded with iron spikes, designed to punch through mail and gouge flesh. Quick enough to be wielded with other weapons, and vicious on a follow-up strike.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Bludgeoning</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6, Bludgeoning or Piercing, Punch, Wound</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6, Bludgeoning or Piercing, Punch, Wound, follow-up strike</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a bonus action, make an additional attack with this weapon at disadvantage. If it hits, the attack deals 2d6 damage instead of the normal damage dice.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bludgeons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a bonus action, make an additional attack at disadvantage. If it hits, it deals 2d6 damage instead of the normal damage dice."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bladed Bow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-recurve-yellow.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An exotic weapon that combines a recurve bow with integrated blade edges along the limbs, allowing the user to slash at close-range threats. Mastery of this weapon allows fluid movement through enemy lines.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6 (60/240), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Heavy, Melee d6, Ranged d8 (120/600), Piercing or Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Heavy, Melee d6, Ranged d8 (120/600), Piercing or Slashing, fluid movement</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>While this weapon is equipped, your movement does not provoke opportunity attacks.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 100, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 120, "long": 600, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "While this weapon is equipped, your movement does not provoke opportunity attacks."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bone Bow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-recurve-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A powerful bow crafted from layered bone and horn, producing extreme draw weight and punishing impact. Its arrows hit with enough force to send targets sprawling. Requires considerable strength to draw effectively.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6 (60/240), Piercing. Requires STR 13.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Ranged d10 (60/240), Piercing or Bludgeoning, Knockback, Stagger. Requires STR 13.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Ranged d10 (60/240), Piercing or Bludgeoning, Knockback (enhanced), Stagger. Requires STR 13.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When an enemy fails their Knockback saving throw, they are pushed 10 feet instead of the normal distance.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 60, "long": 240, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When an enemy fails their Knockback saving throw, they are pushed 10 feet instead of the standard distance."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Collapsible Bow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-short.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An ingeniously engineered bow with folding clockwork limbs, small enough to hide under a coat when collapsed. Devastating against unprepared targets who never saw it coming.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (30/120), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (60/240), Piercing, Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (60/240), Piercing, Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, ambush mastery</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A hit against a surprised creature with this weapon is automatically a critical hit.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 150, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 60, "long": 240, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "A hit against a surprised creature with this weapon is automatically a critical hit."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Compound Bow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-recurve-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A precision-engineered bow with a clockwork cam system that provides mechanical advantage at full draw. Arrows fly with extraordinary force and can punch through multiple enemies in a line at full power.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (100/400), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d10 (200/800), Piercing, Reload (object interaction), Clockwork, Puncture</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d10 (200/800), Piercing, Reload (object interaction), Clockwork, Puncture, Powerful Blow</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Powerful Blow: the attack deals normal damage to the primary target, then the arrow continues in a line and deals full weapon damage to a second target behind the first.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 250, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 200, "long": 800, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Powerful Blow: the attack deals normal damage to the primary target and full weapon damage to a second target in line behind them."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Greatbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/longbow-leather-green.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive warbow that requires exceptional strength to draw, launching arrows with enough force to knock armored knights from their feet. A favorite of elite archers and siege specialists.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing. Requires STR 13.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d10 (200/800), Piercing, Punch, Trip. Requires STR 13.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d10 (200/800), Piercing, Punch, Trip, Mighty Blow. Requires STR 13.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Mighty Blow: the target must save against Knockback. Flying creatures have disadvantage on this saving throw.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 200, "long": 800, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Mighty Blow: the target must save against Knockback. Flying creatures have disadvantage on this saving throw."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Longbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-simple-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>The standard military warbow, capable of launching arrows in excess of six hundred feet. Masters of the longbow learn to compensate for difficult conditions, maintaining accuracy even when the odds are against them.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (120/600), Piercing, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (120/600), Piercing, Keen, disadvantage negation</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If you would have disadvantage on an attack, you may use your bonus action to negate it. You no longer have disadvantage for firing beyond normal range.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 50, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 120, "long": 600, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you would have disadvantage on an attack, use your bonus action to negate it. You no longer suffer disadvantage for firing beyond normal range."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Recurve", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-recurve.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact bow with curved limbs that store more energy per draw, granting superior range and power relative to its size. Master archers use it to engage multiple targets in rapid succession.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing, Steady, multi-target follow-up</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Once per turn, after hitting a target, you may make an additional attack against a different creature within 5 feet of the original target, provided it is also within normal range.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 100, "long": 400, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Once per turn, after hitting a target, make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 feet of the original target that is also within normal range."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Shortbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-short-leather.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A nimble, compact bow suited to skirmishers and scouts who need to fire from horseback or tight quarters. Masters of the shortbow develop a fluid rhythm of fire, loosing arrows faster than opponents can respond.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (60/240), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing, Hipshot</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing, Hipshot, rapid fire</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a bonus action, you may make one attack with this weapon.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 80, "long": 320, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a bonus action, you may make one attack with this weapon."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Yumi", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/bows/bow-recurve-teal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An asymmetric composite bow from eastern traditions, taller than the archer who wields it and shot from a low grip. Highly accurate at range with exceptional technique, and surprisingly effective from the ground at close range.</p><h3>Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing, Sighted</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing, Sighted, fluid targeting</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You gain +2 to attack rolls against a different target from your previous attack. While on foot, you do not suffer disadvantage on attack rolls while prone.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 65, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 100, "long": 400, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Bows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "+2 to attack rolls when targeting a different creature than your previous attack. While on foot, you do not suffer disadvantage on attacks while prone."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Broadsword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_05.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A wide-bladed sword designed for powerful cutting and thrusting attacks. Effective in one hand, the broadsword rewards aggressive fighters who press their advantage.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee 2d4, Keen, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee 2d4, Keen, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 20, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Falchion", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_16.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A single-edged curved blade weighted toward the tip for devastating cleaving strikes. Favored by warriors who rely on raw power to overwhelm their opponents.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d8, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d10, Disarm, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d10, Disarm, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Your powerful blows count as critical hits for the purpose of triggering on-crit effects and resistances.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Your powerful blows count as critical hits for the purpose of triggering on-crit effects and resistances."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Greatsword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_10.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>The quintessential two-handed blade, a greatsword combines reach, power, and precision into a single imposing weapon. Its keen edge and heavy construction let it stagger foes and carve through armor.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Keen, Stagger</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Keen, Stagger — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d12 damage instead of 2d10.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 50, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d12 damage instead of 2d10."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Ikakalaka", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_30.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy chopping sword of island origin, with a broad serrated blade that both deflects incoming blows and punishes enemies who close in. Its weight makes it unforgiving but powerful.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10, Deflect, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10, Deflect, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Deflect now works against ranged attacks. Knockback and Trip effects from this weapon benefit from the Keen property.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 30, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Deflect now works against ranged attacks. Knockback and Trip effects from this weapon benefit from the Keen property."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Katana", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_35.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A gracefully curved blade forged for speed and precision. Equally effective in one or two hands, the katana rewards disciplined fighters who blend offense with defense.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Versatile d8, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Versatile d8, Keen — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Add your proficiency bonus to one-handed Deflect rolls. Two-handed Deflect uses 2d10.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Add your proficiency bonus to one-handed Deflect rolls. Two-handed Deflect uses 2d10."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Khopesh", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_45.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An ancient sickle-sword with an inner hook ideal for disarming and tripping opponents. Light and effective, the khopesh punishes enemies who rely on heavy weapons or sure footing.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee 2d4, Disarm, Keen, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee 2d4, Disarm, Keen, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft and the target has disadvantage on Strength saving throws until the start of your next turn.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft and the target has disadvantage on Strength saving throws until the start of your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Longsword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_08.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>The classic knight's blade, balanced for versatile use in one or two hands. Reliable in all situations, the longsword rewards technical fighters who excel at controlling their opponents.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Versatile d10, Balanced, Disarm</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Versatile d10, Balanced, Disarm — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded one-handed, and 18-20 when wielded two-handed.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded one-handed, and 18-20 when wielded two-handed."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Montante", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_09.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive Iberian two-handed sword used to hold off multiple attackers. Its reach and balance allow a trained fighter to protect companions by denying approach.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a reaction you enter a protective stance. All attacks made against your allies within your reach have disadvantage until the start of your next turn.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a reaction you enter a protective stance. All attacks made against your allies within your reach have disadvantage until the start of your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Odachi", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_12.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An extraordinarily long Japanese field sword built for sweeping strikes against multiple enemies. Masters use its length to chain attacks across the battlefield with devastating efficiency.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Deflect, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Deflect, Keen — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you attack a creature different from the last creature you attacked this turn, you deal an extra damage die on a hit.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 50, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you attack a creature different from the last creature you attacked this turn, you deal an extra damage die on a hit."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Scimitar", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_13.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A curved cavalry blade designed to deliver slashing blows on the move. The scimitar rewards aggressive fighters who keep their momentum, hitting harder after closing distance.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Deflect, Riposte</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Deflect, Riposte — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If you travel 20 ft or more before attacking (including while mounted), your next attack with this weapon deals an extra d8 damage.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you travel 20 ft or more before attacking (including while mounted), your next attack with this weapon deals an extra d8 damage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Short Glaive", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_40.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact polearm-style blade combining a glaive's cutting edge with a sword's maneuverability. The short glaive enables mobile fighters to brace against charges, lunge forward, and disengage without opening themselves to counterattack.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee 2d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee 3d4, Balanced, Brace, Lunge</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee 3d4, Balanced, Brace, Lunge — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you take the Dash action, you do not provoke opportunity attacks and may make one attack at any point during your movement.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 3, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you take the Dash action, you do not provoke opportunity attacks and may make one attack at any point during your movement."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Sword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_06.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy, wide-bladed two-handed sword built to stagger armored opponents and cleave through large enemies. Brutal and reliable, it is the weapon of front-line soldiers who need guaranteed stopping power.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d12, Stagger</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d12, Stagger — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded two-handed. Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d8 (or 2d10 two-handed) instead of d12 (or 2d8 two-handed).</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 30, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Combat Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded two-handed. Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d8 (or 2d10 two-handed) instead of d12 (or 2d8 two-handed)."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Grapple Crossbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy mechanized crossbow that fires a grapple bolt trailing a strong cable. Beyond dealing damage, it can entangle, trip, and restrain targets — or pull them toward the user.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6+4 (80/320), Reload bonus, Clockwork, Entangle, Keen, Punch, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6+4 (80/320), Reload bonus, Clockwork, Entangle, Keen, Punch, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Targets have disadvantage on ability checks to resist the Entangle pull. You may choose to fire the grapple bolt without dealing damage.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 175, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 13, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": "4"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 80, "long": 320, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Targets have disadvantage on ability checks to resist the Entangle pull. You may choose to fire the grapple bolt without dealing damage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Hand Crossbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-simple-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact one-handed crossbow that fires with surprising force at close range. Its clockwork reload mechanism and hipshot capability make it a favorite for mobile skirmishers and ambushers.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d4 (30/120), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d6+2 (30/120), Reload free, Hipshot, Keen, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d6+2 (30/120), Reload free, Hipshot, Keen, Steady — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You can reload this crossbow one-handed. If you have not used your Attack action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "2"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can reload this crossbow one-handed. If you have not used your Attack action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Heavy Crossbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-worn.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A powerful siege-weight crossbow that punches through armor and knocks enemies off their feet. Skilled users can react to enemies trying to close or escape, turning the weapon into a battlefield deterrent.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d10+4 (100/400), Reload bonus, Keen, Puncture, Sighted, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d10+4 (100/400), Reload bonus, Keen, Puncture, Sighted, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 50, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 8, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "4"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 100, "long": 400, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Hidden Crossbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-simple-worn.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A tiny spring-loaded crossbow affixed to the wrist or forearm, concealed beneath a sleeve or glove. It fires with a flick of the wrist, ideal for assassins and spies who need a deniable ranged option at close range.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged d4 (20/60), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged d4+1 (20/60), Reload object interaction, Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, Keen, Slip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged d4+1 (20/60), Reload object interaction, Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, Keen, Slip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you miss an attack with this weapon, you may use your reaction to make another attack against the same target.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 150, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "1"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you miss an attack with this weapon, you may use your reaction to make another attack against the same target."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Light Crossbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A reliable two-handed crossbow balancing rate of fire and range. Sighted and steady, it suits disciplined marksmen who fire from prepared positions and punish enemies who try to close the distance.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8+3 (80/320), Reload reaction, Keen, Punch, Steady, Sighted</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8+3 (80/320), Reload reaction, Keen, Punch, Steady, Sighted — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "3"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 80, "long": 320, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Mauler", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A short-ranged multi-bolt crossbow that fires a spread of bolts in a tight pattern. At close range it is devastating, shredding through flesh and punching through light armor with every volley.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d4 (20/80), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 3d4+3 (20/80), Reload bonus, Hipshot, Keen, Puncture</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 3d4+3 (20/80), Reload bonus, Hipshot, Keen, Puncture — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>The Puncture property now activates when any individual die shows a 3 or 4, in addition to its normal triggers.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 100, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 3, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "3"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 80, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "The Puncture property now activates when any individual die shows a 3 or 4, in addition to its normal triggers."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Portable Ballista", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-ornate.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A man-portable siege weapon that fires massive bolts capable of pinning targets to terrain and restraining entire groups. Slow to load but catastrophically powerful, it dominates open ground.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (150/600), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 2d6+5 (150/600), Reload attack, Entangle, Keen, Knockback, Punch, Puncture, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 2d6+5 (150/600), Reload attack, Entangle, Keen, Knockback, Punch, Puncture, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A successful Entangle also applies the restrained condition and pins the target to the terrain until freed.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 500, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 15, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "5"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 150, "long": 600, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "A successful Entangle also applies the restrained condition and pins the target to the terrain until freed."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Repeating Crossbow", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-ornate-red.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A magazine-fed crossbow that fires repeatedly without manual reloading. In trained hands it becomes a weapon of sustained fire superiority — at the cost of the user's movement.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Reload free, Keen, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Reload free, Keen, Steady — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you take the Attack action, you may make one additional attack as a bonus action. If you do, your speed becomes 0 until the start of your next turn.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 150, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 80, "long": 320, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you take the Attack action, you may make one additional attack as a bonus action. If you do, your speed becomes 0 until the start of your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Spinner", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-simple-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A clockwork rotary crossbow that fires razor discs rather than bolts. On full auto it can hit multiple nearby targets with a single trigger pull, making it ideal for crowd control.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (30/120), Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d4 (30/120), Reload free, Clockwork, Disarm, Keen, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d4 (30/120), Reload free, Clockwork, Disarm, Keen, Steady — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As an action, choose a number of targets up to your Intelligence modifier (minimum 1) each within 10 ft of the first target. Make a single attack roll against all of them, dealing damage to each you hit.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 100, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Crossbows", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As an action, choose a number of targets up to your Intelligence modifier (minimum 1) each within 10 ft of the first target. Make a single attack roll against all of them, dealing damage to each you hit."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Cutlass", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_04.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A short, slightly curved naval blade built for close-quarters fighting. Equally at home on a ship deck or a city street, the cutlass rewards fighters who press relentlessly forward.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Deflect, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Deflect, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Dagger", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_20.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>The universal sidearm of adventurers everywhere. Concealable, throwable, and deadly in skilled hands, the dagger is as much a tool as a weapon — and masters make it terrifyingly effective.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Balanced, Conceal</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Balanced, Conceal — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You may make one additional attack with this weapon as a bonus action.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You may make one additional attack with this weapon as a bonus action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Estoc", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_11.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long, stiff thrusting sword built to punch through plate armor and chainmail. The estoc has no cutting edge — only a rigid triangular or square blade that concentrates force on a needle point.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Brace, Punch, Wound</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Brace, Punch, Wound — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If you have not used your Attack action or held action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you have not used your Attack action or held action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Kukri", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_03.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A forward-curving Nepalese blade that chops as well as it slices. Throwable and light, the kukri excels at hamstringing enemies and leaving them unable to flee or fight effectively.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/40), Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Thrown (40/80), Keen, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Thrown (40/80), Keen, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft. The target must make a Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns to end the effect.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 80, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft. The target must make a Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns to end the effect."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Rapier", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_25.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>The weapon of choice for duelists and swashbucklers. Long, slender, and supremely precise, the rapier rewards fighters who commit fully to its use — punishing armor and keeping the blade in constant motion.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Puncture, Riposte</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Puncture, Riposte — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If wielding only a rapier (no shield or other weapon), add d4 to your damage rolls. If dual wielding with a Light weapon, gain +1 to AC from weapon deflection.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If wielding only a rapier (no shield or other weapon), add d4 to your damage rolls. If dual wielding with a Light weapon, gain +1 to AC from weapon deflection."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Saber", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_07.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A curved cavalry sword as elegant as it is deadly. The saber's slight flex and razor edge let it turn aside attacks and deliver lightning counterstrikes — masters who dual wield them become engines of relentless offense.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Deflect, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Deflect, Keen — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Add d4 to Deflect rolls. While wielding two sabers, when you reduce an enemy to 0 HP you regain your reaction immediately.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 35, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Add d4 to Deflect rolls. While wielding two sabers, when you reduce an enemy to 0 HP you regain your reaction immediately."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Sai", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_01.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A pronged iron weapon designed to catch and disarm blades. Small enough to conceal, the sai turns defense into offense — a miss against the sai's wielder may cost the attacker their own weapon.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Conceal, Deflect, Nimble</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Conceal, Deflect, Nimble — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You gain +1 to AC while wielding this weapon. When an enemy misses you with a melee attack, they must succeed on a Strength or Dexterity saving throw or drop their weapon.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You gain +1 to AC while wielding this weapon. When an enemy misses you with a melee attack, they must succeed on a Strength or Dexterity saving throw or drop their weapon."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Shortsword", "type": "weapon", "img": "modules/rnk-commanders-rme/assets/swords/sword_14.png", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact, well-balanced blade suited to close quarters and ambush fighting. Mastered, the shortsword's balance becomes an active combat tool — advantage lets the weapon truly shine.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Balanced</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Balanced — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>The Balanced property now also applies to attackers targeting you. When you have advantage on an attack roll, roll your damage dice and Balanced dice twice and use the better result.</td></tr></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": null, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Dueling Blades", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "The Balanced property now also applies to attackers targeting you. When you have advantage on an attack roll, roll your damage dice and Balanced dice twice and use the better result."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Fire Knuckle", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact firearm affixed to a gauntlet, combining close-quarters striking power with a short-range shot.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Melee d6, Ranged d4+5 (10/20), Reload (action), Firearm</td><td>Clockwork, Hipshot, Steady, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 750, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": 20, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fir", "rel"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you hit with a melee attack, the next ranged attack made this turn with this weapon against the same creature has advantage and counts as a critical hit."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Arquebus", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-musket-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long, heavy two-handed firearm capable of devastating ranged fire and fitted with a bayonet for close combat.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 2d10+5 (300/900), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Punch, Puncture, Sighted</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 500, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 10, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "+5"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 300, "long": 900, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can arm the bayonet with an object interaction and the arquebus gains Brace, Double Ended d6, Finesse, Reach."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Blunderbuss", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-blunderbuss-bronze.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A wide-mouthed, short-ranged firearm that unleashes a devastating spread of shot, capable of knocking enemies off their feet.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d8+5 (40/60), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Knockback, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 300, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "+5"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On hit, a target within 15 ft must succeed on a Strength saving throw or becomes your choice of pushed back 5ft or prone."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Firelance", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-musket-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A polearm-mounted firearm that can both stab in melee and unleash a cone of fire at close range.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d12, Ranged d10 (15 ft cone), Reload (bonus action), Firearm</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 200, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["piercing", "fire"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 15, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "fir", "rel"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As an action, you sweep the lance around you, forcing all creatures within 10 ft to succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or become blinded until the end of their next turn. The weapon must be loaded to use this action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Gunblade", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A hybrid weapon combining a blade with a built-in firearm, allowing seamless transitions between melee and ranged combat.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Ranged 2d6+5 (40/160), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Hipshot, Steady</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 350, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 160, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can make one additional attack as part of your Attack action. If you made a ranged attack with this weapon, then this additional attack must be a melee attack. If you made a melee attack with this weapon, then this additional attack must be a ranged attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Hand Cannon", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-hand-cannon.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy one-handed firearm delivering powerful shots at range with good accuracy.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Ranged 2d6+5 (80/320), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Hipshot, Puncture, Sighted, Steady</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 250, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "+5"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 80, "long": 320, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a bonus action, you can make an attack with this weapon if you haven't used the attack action or held your action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Pepperbox", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-ornate-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact multi-barreled firearm that can be easily concealed and fires multiple shots in rapid succession.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d4+5 (30/120), Reload (action), Firearm</td><td>Conceal, Hipshot</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 1000, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": "+5"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt", "fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As an action you fire all barrels at once, ignoring Reload and rolling an attack for each loaded barrel. The weapon is destroyed if you roll a 1, but could be repaired with smith's tools."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Portable Cannon", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-blunderbuss-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive shoulder-mounted cannon capable of devastating long-range bombardment, staggering and sundering armor on impact.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 3d10+5 (200/800), Reload (action), Firearm</td><td>Knockback, Sighted, Stagger, Sunder</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 750, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 12, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 3, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": "+5"}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 200, "long": 800, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can choose to overpack your weapon when you Reload, spending three uses of gunpowder. When you fire the cannon, all creatures in a 15ft cone must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or be blinded and deafened until the start of their next turn. If you roll a 1 on your attack roll when you overpack, the cannon is destroyed but could be repaired later with smith's tools."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Wrist Rocket", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-worn.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A clockwork firearm strapped to the wrist, easily concealed and triggered with a nimble flick for surprise fire.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged 2d4 (range varies), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, Nimble, Steady</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 150, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["fire"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fir", "rel", "amm"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Firearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If an enemy you can see misses you with an attack, you can use your reaction to make an attack against that enemy."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Claw Flail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/flail-ball-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A light flail tipped with hooked claws, capable of entangling and wounding enemies with quick, nimble strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6</td><td>Clockwork, Entangle, Nimble, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 35, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you land an attack using your Conceal property, the enemy cannot make a saving throw against your entangle attack, and suffers disadvantage on its saving throw against any other use of your Weapon DC."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Double Flail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy flail with spiked heads on both ends, designed to batter through defenses and punish enemies even on disadvantaged swings.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d4, Versatile 2d6</td><td>Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 20, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 7, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "ver"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you suffer disadvantage but one dice would have hit, you deal 1 of the weapon's damage dice plus your Strength modifier, even though this still counts as a miss. If you have advantage and both dice hit, add your Strength modifier twice to the damage total."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Great Flail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/flail-triple-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive two-handed flail with reach, capable of knocking back enemies and even sundering their shields.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d12, Reach</td><td>Knockback, Punch, Reach, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 12, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can attack an adjacent target if your attack misses the first target. If the enemy is wielding a shield, your successful sunder disarms them of it, in addition to lowering AC."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Heavy Flail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A reliable one-handed flail that can be used two-handed for greater damage, with entangling and punching capabilities.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Versatile d10</td><td>Entangle, Punch, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "ver"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If your target successfully saves against your weapon DC, you can make a weapon attack as part of the same action. This additional attack must be a normal weapon attack, and cannot be a property attack forcing another saving throw."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Light Flail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/flail-ball-worn.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A quick, light flail suited for disarming and tripping opponents with agile, one-handed strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6</td><td>Disarm, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 8, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can reroll any attack you miss, but must take the new result."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Nunchaku", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/clubs/club-baton-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A pair of handles connected by a short chain, wielded with finesse to conceal, entangle, and trip opponents.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4</td><td>Conceal, Entangle, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can use the Double Ended property one-handed. Dual wielding two nunchaku, you can attack twice with Double Ended."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Pole Flail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/flail-spiked-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long-hafted flail with reach, capable of entangling and knocking back enemies while preventing opportunity attacks.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee d10</td><td>Entangle, Knockback, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 10, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you make a melee attack against a creature, you don't provoke opportunity attacks from that creature for the rest of the turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Rope Hammer", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A weighted hammer on a rope, used with finesse to entangle and trip foes, and to deflect incoming strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6</td><td>Entangle, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you roll a Deflect roll, you can make an attack as part of the same reaction."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Spring Mace", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/maces/mace-spiked-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A clockwork mace with an extending spring mechanism that grants surprising reach and a powerful first strike with knockback.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Reach, Melee d8</td><td>Clockwork, Knockback, Stagger, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "The first time during an encounter you use Reach or Lunge with this weapon, your attack gains advantage. If this attack hits, it deals weapon damage and your enemy must make a saving throw with disadvantage against the Knockback property."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Trisectional Staff", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/staves/staff-orb-red.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A three-section staff with flexible joints, granting finesse and reach while entangling and tripping enemies.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Reach, Melee d6, Double Ended d4</td><td>Entangle, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "fin", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Flails", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Your Disarm, Entangle, and Trip attacks can deal bludgeoning damage equal to your Dexterity modifier, instead of Strength."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Great Pick", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A massive two-handed war pick designed to punch through armor, barb into flesh, and inflict grievous wounds.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6</td><td>Barbed, Entangle, Puncture, Punch, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Your Wound property uses 2d8 instead of a single d8 weapon damage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Light Hammer", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-light-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A small, throwable hammer suitable for quick strikes in melee or at range, delivering punishing blows.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6, Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Punch</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you score a mighty blow, your enemy suffers a d4 penalty to their next Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom saving throw. When you score a critical hit, the enemy suffers a d6 penalty to their next saving throw of any ability."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Light Pick", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/pick-mining-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A small, light pick that can be thrown, used to pierce, slip past defenses, and trip enemies with quick finesse attacks.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Punch, Puncture, Slip, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Your piercing damage perk gains +2 to attack, rather than +1."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Lucerne", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-crescent-glowing.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long polearm combining hammer and pick heads, with reach for bracing against charges and sundering armor.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6</td><td>Brace, Punch, Puncture, Sunder, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 8, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If your enemy succeeds on the save from your Sunder, they instead take normal weapon damage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Maul", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-war-metal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A great two-handed war hammer that sends enemies flying with devastating knockback and staggering force.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6</td><td>Knockback, Punch, Stagger, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 12, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On hit, you can move a same size or smaller enemy 5ft, and your Knockback moves 10ft. You count as one size category larger for Knockback."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Stiletto", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-stiletto-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A slender, easily concealed piercing weapon designed to punch through gaps in armor with precise, deadly thrusts.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4</td><td>Conceal, Punch, Puncture</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can use a bonus action to attempt to shove a creature you are entangling."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Wall Pick", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-bronze.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A light pick designed to hook into surfaces and enemies alike, entangling and wounding foes with barbed strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Barbed, Entangle, Punch, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If your Entangle misses, you can reroll the attack but must take the new roll. If you score a powerful blow, your enemy is restrained and grappled."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Hammer", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-war-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A versatile war hammer that can be used one- or two-handed, capable of punishing blows, staggering, and sundering armor.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Versatile d10</td><td>Punch, Stagger, Sunder</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["ver"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you move at least 10 ft in a straight line before your attack, your Sunder can lower an enemy's AC by -2 with one hand, or -3 with two hands."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Mallet", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-double-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy one-handed mallet that delivers crushing knockback and staggering blows, overwhelming enemies when wielded with advantage.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10</td><td>Knockback, Punch, Stagger</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 20, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you have advantage, the saves to resist your weapon DC are made with disadvantage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Pick", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-worn.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A one-handed war pick that punctures armor, wounds, and trips enemies, with a unique escalating bleed wound mechanic.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8</td><td>Punch, Puncture, Sunder, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Hammers & Picks", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you Wound, roll a d10. The enemy takes that damage instead of the normal Wound mechanics, and each round after that, it takes 1 fewer damage. You can refresh this Wound with a higher roll than the damage the enemy took on its previous turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Atlatl", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/javelin-tip-glowing-teal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A throwing board used to hurl darts or javelins with great force. The atlatl extends the thrower's arm, providing additional leverage and range.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> One-Handed, Ranged d8 (100/300), Reload (object interaction), Punch</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 100, "long": 300, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "rel"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you score a mighty blow, before the target's next turn, the next attack against this target gains advantage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Blowgun", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/ammunition/arrow-head-war-pointed.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long tube used to shoot small darts by blowing air through it. Favored by those who value stealth and the ability to deliver poisons from a distance.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Light, One-Handed, Ranged d4 (25/100), Reload (free), Conceal, Hipshot</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 25, "long": 100, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can load two darts and shoot two with the same attack roll at the same target or to two targets that are within 5 feet of one another. Each dart can deliver a poison or other payload, and when this weapon delivers poison, the enemy suffers disadvantage on the saving throw. Apply your ability modifier to damage on only one dart."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Portable Catapult", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/slings/sling-simple-leather.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact, deployable siege device capable of hurling heavy projectiles at enemies. Once set up, it can unleash devastating barrages of ammunition.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Affixed, Heavy, Ranged 2d8 (150/600), Reload (attack action), Knockback, Punch, Stagger, Trip</p>"}, "price": {"value": 175, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 20, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 150, "long": 600, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "hvy", "two", "rel"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can load a full container of ammunition, e.g. 20 arrows or 50 needles, into the basket. As an action, you pick a point in range and release the basket. Each creature within a 20 ft radius cylinder, 60ft high centered on your point must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking a number of weapon damage dice equal to your proficiency bonus on a failed save, or half on a success."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Rope Dart", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/dart-feathered-yellow.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A weighted dart attached to a long rope, allowing the wielder to strike enemies at range and then retrieve the weapon. Its flexible nature enables a variety of combat techniques.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (20/50), Brace, Conceal, Entangle, Hipshot, Puncture</p>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 50, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can Brace as a bonus action and make a number of Brace attacks without using your reaction equal to your proficiency bonus before the start of your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Sling", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A simple but effective ranged weapon consisting of a pouch attached to two cords. Stones or lead bullets are whirled and released at high velocity. Can also be used as a melee weapon.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Ranged d8 (150/600), Reload (free), Conceal, Disarm</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 150, "long": 600, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On a mighty blow, the target must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or suffer disadvantage to attacks until the end of its next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Sling Staff", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/slings/sling-leather-black.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A staff with a sling cup at one end, allowing both melee and ranged attacks. The staff's length also enables the Double Ended technique, striking with the opposite end.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Melee d6, Ranged d6 (150/600), Reload (free), Double Ended d8, Entangle</p>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 150, "long": 600, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Your Double Ended attacks deal weapon damage plus your Strength modifier to your grappled target, and still automatically hit."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Sling Tube", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A rigid tube-shaped sling capable of launching various types of ammunition including bullets, bolts, and arrows. The tube's design allows for a wide spread of fire.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (60/180), Reload (object interaction), Conceal, Hipshot</p><p><em>Damage types: Bludgeoning, Piercing, or Slashing depending on ammunition used.</em></p>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 60, "long": 180, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "two", "rel"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can pack up to a full container of ammunition into the sling tube. As an action, you can launch all the ammunition in a 30 foot cone. Each creature in the cone must make a Dexterity saving throw. A target takes a number of weapon dice damage equal to your proficiency bonus on a failed save, or none on a success."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Wrist Shot", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/slings/sling-simple-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A compact wrist-mounted sling device, leaving the hands free while providing a concealed ranged attack option. Its surprising nature can catch enemies off guard.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (40/160), Disarm, Hipshot</p>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 160, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialR", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["amm", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Launch Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you score a mighty blow, your enemy loses its reaction until the start of its next turn. If you score a powerful blow, this effect applies, as well as all attacks against this enemy gain advantage until the end of your next turn. On a critical hit, these effects both apply."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bite", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/creatures/claws/mouth-teeth-long-red.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's jaws and teeth. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee, Entangle, Nimble, Wound</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can make a single bite attack as part of that action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Claw", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/creatures/claws/claw-curved-teal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's claws. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee, Keen, Nimble, Wound</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you take the Attack action and hit with a melee attack, you can count that attack as a critical hit. Once you use this ability you cannot do so again until you finish a short rest."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Horns", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/creatures/abilities/ram-horns-red.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's horns or antlers. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Natural, Melee, Brace, Punch, Puncture, Sunder</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you move at least 20 feet in a straight line toward your target, you can make one melee attack with your horns as a bonus action. If this attack hits, your weapon damage dice is doubled."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Slam", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A powerful natural weapon attack using the creature's body mass — a fist, foot, or whole body impact. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Heavy, Natural, Melee, Brace, Disarm, Stagger</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you move at least 20ft straight toward an enemy and hit with a slam attack in the same turn, that enemy must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be knocked prone and you can make an additional slam attack as a bonus action."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Tail", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/creatures/abilities/tail-swipe-green.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's tail. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Natural, Reach, Melee, Double Ended (one dice size smaller), Knockback, Trip</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As an action, you can attack all enemies within 5 feet of you."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Tentacle", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/creatures/claws/tentacle-kraken-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's tentacle or appendage. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Light, Natural, Melee, Entangle, Trip</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When your target fails a saving throw against your Entangle attack, they become restrained and grappled."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Unarmed Strike", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using fists, feet, head, or any other part of the body. Damage is 1d4 + Strength modifier bludgeoning damage. RME properties apply on top of the base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee d4, Nimble</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "simpleM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can make an Unarmed strike as an off-hand attack even if your hands are occupied. You can spend a bonus action to shove or perform a Disarm attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Wings", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/creatures/abilities/wing-bat-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's wings to batter and buffet foes. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee, Deflect d6, Knockback, Trip</p>"}, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 0, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Natural Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As long as you do not already have disadvantage on your attack rolls, when you make your first attack on your turn, you can decide to attack defensively. Doing so gives you disadvantage on all weapon attack rolls during this turn, but attack rolls against you have disadvantage until your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bladed Staff", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-flared-purple.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long staff with sharpened blades at both ends, allowing for swift and precise attacks. Its balanced design makes it equally effective at thrusting and sweeping strikes.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Reach, Melee 2d4, Double Ended d4, Balanced</p>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you use the Double Ended property, you do not need to be within 5ft of your target."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Glaive", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/glaive-hooked-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long pole weapon with a single-edged blade on one end. The glaive's reach and versatility make it a fearsome weapon against multiple opponents, particularly effective against large creatures.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced, Brace</p>"}, "price": {"value": 20, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Against creatures of category size Large and larger, your damage is 3d6 instead of 2d6. Your Double Ended attack becomes 2d4."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Guisarme", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-hooked.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A pole weapon with a curved blade designed for hooking and tripping opponents. Its heavy head delivers devastating blows while its hook can tear mounted riders from their saddles.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee d12, Brace, Entangle, Trip</p>"}, "price": {"value": 20, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Your trip attacks impose disadvantage on saving throws made to resist them and if you succeed on a trip attack against a mounted enemy, it is automatically dismounted and lands prone in an unoccupied space of your choice within 5ft of its mount."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Lajatang", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-broad-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A double-ended polearm with crescent-shaped blades at both ends. A weapon of rare elegance and deadly efficiency, demanding exceptional skill to master its spinning defensive and offensive techniques.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Heavy, Reach, Melee d10, Double Ended d10, Brace</p>"}, "price": {"value": 75, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 8, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "On your turn, you can spend your reaction to enter a Defensive Stance, negating any flanking bonus or ability any enemy might have for flanking you or having the enemy's ally near you, such as pack tactics or sneak attack. You can use Double Ended twice on your turn, but your second attack must be against a different target than your first."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Naginata", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/glaive-winged-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A Japanese-style curved blade mounted on a long pole. Light and swift, the naginata's keen edge and reach make it a weapon of grace and precision, capable of deflecting incoming attacks.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced, Keen</p>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can add your proficiency bonus to your Deflect roll."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Partisan", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-winged-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy polearm with a broad blade and side prongs designed to catch and deflect enemy weapons. The partisan combines offensive reach with exceptional defensive capabilities.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Brace, Deflect, Riposte</p>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You have +1 weapon AC. When an enemy lands an attack on an ally within your range, you can use your reaction to force the enemy to reroll the attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Scythe", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/scythe-curved-teal.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A farming scythe adapted for use as a weapon of war, with the blade straightened or reset parallel to the shaft. Its sweeping cuts can carry through multiple targets.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d4, Entangle, Keen, Puncture, Trip</p>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 8, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["hvy", "rch", "two"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Polearms", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you reduce an enemy to 0 hit points with slashing damage, you can choose to apply the remaining damage to any other target within your range, instead of only adjacent targets."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Godendag", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy staff topped with a spiked iron ball, the godendag combines the reach of a spear with the crushing power of a mace.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 12, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you score a mighty blow, the next attack against this target gains advantage."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Hand Spear", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/javelin-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A short, balanced spear designed for one-handed use, equally suited for melee combat and throwing.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 40, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you make a second attack on your turn against the same creature, that attack has advantage and you ignore all sources of disadvantage for that attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Harpoon", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/trident-silver.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy barbed spear designed to pierce and lodge in flesh, preventing escape. Favored by hunters and fishermen alike.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 11, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You drag an enemy toward you a number of feet equal to twice your Strength score, and your target suffers disadvantage to Strength saving throws while it is impaled."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Javelin", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/javelin-pointed-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A light throwing spear balanced for long-range accuracy. Javelins are a staple of soldiers and hunters across the world.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you score a mighty blow, the target suffers a -2 AC penalty. On its turn an enemy can use an action to succeed on a Strength saving throw to pry the javelin free, destroying it in the process."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Lance", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/lance-steel-spiraled.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long cavalry weapon designed to be used from horseback, the lance delivers devastating charges and keeps foes at bay.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can attempt a Shove as a bonus action. While mounted, after you successfully hit a target, you can attempt a shove as part of the attack and gain advantage in the roll. Additionally, you no longer suffer disadvantage to attack rolls when you use this weapon on foot."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Pike", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-crescent-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An extremely long polearm used in tight formations, the pike keeps enemies at a distance and can brace against charges.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 8, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 12, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You ignore half cover. Additionally, if you hit with an attack on a target more than 5 ft away, it cannot move closer to you until the end of its next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Ravenbeak", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-hooked-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>An elegantly crafted spear with a hooked blade resembling a raven's beak, designed to disarm foes and riposte swiftly.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "ver", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you hit with an attack, you can move your target 5 ft in a direction of your choice, and it can't move closer to you until the start of your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Trident", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/trident-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A three-pronged spear used both on land and at sea, the trident's multiple points are excellent for catching and disarming opponents.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 2, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["ver", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can Deflect attacks against any target in reach. When you wield a trident with two hands, your enemy must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be disarmed when you Deflect."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Spear", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-broad-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A versatile combat spear reinforced for the rigors of war, featuring a double-ended design that rewards skilled wielders.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["ver", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you use this weapon one-handed, you can use Double Ended as if you were using it with two hands. In two hands, you deal an extra d4 weapon damage each time you hit with the main melee attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Winged Spear", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/polearms/spear-winged-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A spear with cross-guards or 'wings' near the blade that prevent over-penetration and allow for deflecting and repositioning opponents.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 25, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "ver", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Spears", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you hit with an attack, you can move your target 5 ft in a direction of your choice, and it can't move closer to you until the start of your next turn."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bladewing", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/boomerang-pointed-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A large, heavy bladed disc that returns after being thrown. In skilled hands it can cut through entire formations of enemies.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 60, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "hvy", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Once on your turn, using one of your attacks, you can make an attack against all creatures in a 30 foot line, 5 feet wide, before the bladewing returns."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Bolas", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/bolas-leather.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>Weighted balls connected by cord, the bolas are thrown to entangle and trip opponents, restraining them in place.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 30, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When your Entangle attack hits, the target must succeed on the save or become prone and restrained."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Boomerang", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/boomerang-wood.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A curved throwing weapon that returns to the thrower when it misses. Useful for striking multiple targets in a single throw.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "Once on your turn, you can choose two targets within 40ft to attack with the same attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Chakram", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/chakram-pointed-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A flat circular blade with a sharpened outer edge, the chakram is both a melee weapon and a deadly thrown disc.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If a creature misses you with an attack, as a reaction you can attack that creature."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Dart", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/dart-poison.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A small, weighted needle that can be thrown with surprising accuracy. Often used to deliver poisons or pin enemies in place.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.05, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can deal no damage on hit and pin the enemy to an adjacent wall or obstacle causing your enemy to be restrained. The escape DC is your weapon DC."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Kunai", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/knife-kunai-black.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A multi-purpose blade used for throwing, climbing, and close combat. Its ring pommel allows for spinning deflection techniques.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.25, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can use Deflect within your normal range, and for any creature of your choice."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Mambele", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/axe-thrown-pointed.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A multi-bladed throwing knife with curved secondary blades, the mambele tumbles in flight and can deflect incoming attacks.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 40, "long": 120, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you Deflect any damage from a melee weapon, you can Wound your enemy."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Net", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/net-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A weighted net thrown to entangle opponents. The net itself deals no damage but can incapacitate enemies effectively.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 0, "denomination": 1, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": 20, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["two", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "The net's AC is equal to your weapon DC. If you have advantage on an Entangle attack, your target has disadvantage on the check made to escape."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Throwing Knife", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/knife-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A balanced blade optimized for throwing, the throwing knife can be used in melee or launched to distract and hobble enemies.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 30, "long": 90, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can deal only your Strength or Dexterity modifier in damage, but force your target to succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or lose its reaction and suffer disadvantage on its next attack."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Throwing Shot", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/ball-iron-black.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A heavy iron ball thrown with tremendous force, the throwing shot staggers and knocks down enemies through sheer impact.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 6, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you score a critical hit or have advantage and both rolls would have hit, your enemy must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or be stunned until the end of its next turn. If you have disadvantage but one dice would have hit, deal your Strength modifier in damage, though this still counts as a miss."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Throwing Star", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/shuriken-steel.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A small multi-pointed metal disc that can be thrown with deadly accuracy. Easy to conceal and carry in quantity.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 1, "denomination": "sp"}, "weight": {"value": 0.05, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 20, "long": 60, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "lgt", "thr"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Throwing Weapons", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As an action, you can make a single attack against all targets of your choice within 20 ft of you. You must have enough throwing stars to attack each target."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Kusarigama", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/hook-steel-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A sickle attached to a weighted chain, the kusarigama can entangle and trip opponents before striking with the blade.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 30, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 4, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you hit with a main attack and Double Ended attack on the same target on the same turn, you can move your target 5 ft in a direction of your choosing."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Meteor Hammer", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/flail-ball-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A weighted ball on a long flexible chain, the meteor hammer can be used to entangle, trip, or lunge at distant foes.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["bludgeoning"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "As a reaction you can enter a readied stance. Until the start of your next turn, you can make an attack against any creature that enters your reach, and doing so does not use your reaction."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Scorpion Whip", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A flexible whip tipped with sharp spines like a scorpion's tail, capable of entangling and puncturing opponents at reach.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 5, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "If you choose a different target than your previous attack, the attack roll gains +2."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Scourge", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-red.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A multi-tailed whip with weighted or barbed ends, the scourge deals terrible lacerating wounds and excels at disarming foes.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 3, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": [], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "This weapon adds two extra damage dice when it scores a critical hit. When an enemy is affected by the Wound property, it takes two damage dice."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Spiked Chain", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/chain-spiked-grey.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A length of chain with sharpened spikes, the spiked chain can disarm, entangle, and build momentum with each successive strike.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 10, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 5, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you miss, add another damage die to the next attack that hits. At the end of your turn, any extra built up damage dice are lost."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "War Poi", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-blue.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>Weighted balls on chains that are lit aflame, the war poi combine the reach and entangling properties of flexible weapons with burning fire damage.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 6, "types": ["bludgeoning", "fire"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you use a property attack, you always deal the fire damage listed."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Whip", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-brown.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A long leather lash with an extended reach of 15 feet, the whip excels at disarming, entangling, and tripping opponents from a safe distance.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 2, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 1, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 15, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "When you Disarm, you can place the item anywhere in your reach, or use your reaction to catch it. An item that can be grabbed with the whip can be placed anywhere else in your reach."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Whip Dagger", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-black.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A flexible blade that can strike like a whip, the whip dagger can entangle enemies and then exploit that vulnerability to deliver precise strikes.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 15, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 2, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 4, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": null}, "range": {"value": 10, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "two", "rch"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "While an enemy is entangled, you can attack it or any target within 5ft of it. This forgoes the automatic hit granted by the Entangle property, and if this attack hits, it deals weapon damage and your ability modifier."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
{"name": "Whip Sword", "type": "weapon", "img": "icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-gold.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>A segmented blade that can be wielded as a rigid sword or released to flow like a whip. Sword Form: a precise one-handed blade. Whip Form: a flexible reach weapon that entangles and trips.</p>"}, "price": {"value": 150, "denomination": "gp"}, "weight": {"value": 3, "units": "lb"}, "damage": {"base": {"number": 1, "denomination": 8, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}, "versatile": {"number": 1, "denomination": 10, "types": ["piercing", "slashing"], "bonus": ""}}, "range": {"value": 5, "long": null, "units": "ft"}, "type": {"value": "martialM", "baseItem": ""}, "properties": ["fin", "ver"], "equipped": false}, "effects": [], "flags": {"rnk-commanders-rme": {"rmeData": {"group": "Whips", "trainingLevel": "basic", "masterPerk": "You can change between weapon forms freely. Additionally, when you hit with this weapon, you can deal only your Strength modifier in damage and automatically Entangle your enemy by changing to its whip profile."}}}, "_stats": {"systemId": "dnd5e", "systemVersion": "5.2.5"}}
